**version 0.1.3**

Bugfixes:
> no more crashes on connection loss
> menu now closes after timeout
> all send out units will be recovered if the bot crashes
> The correct time for building units is now displayed
> Added warning message when trying to start a second build thread in a military building
> Building units costs resources when starting to build them
> When the bot crashes the resources invested in current unit training will be restored

Changes:
> Menu timeout set to 30 seconds

New Features:
> Send unit menu point in rally units submenu
> Added custom resource emojis
